ca, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;乔·拜登（Joe Biden）被诊断出&lt;/strong&gt;患有&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/edr8slBNpD1HS3kjprEIUui9dTdrNAqZ6AvVVk7fTVCwobwbSQo-ho0PqvqNdr8WVP27OFBDAvtqEgafOcO2b-rwE9O674Gcih7hXzPjdSxocLLPaJ5XWR-0k_3_cW9HHgR-wpNO_BcGuNxJEG1zz03-eRchSbnl95Sip5m0xkacg57rNC4qDNOfyf5_KiimBP7D9c7fk2BGR7qFWb6lSEGJbU7shii9WudWBnCSRYpCQ5jUMalKdzdqzQidsM5SSTLSz_pO_oEC719R5sWn3fMERg/xXPMJPB5Qpa3oQCk2e31RoYEMqMd2Jbg/9" target="_blank"&gt;侵略性的前列腺癌形式&lt;/a&gt;，该癌症已经传播到他的骨头上。前总统82岁，正在与他的医疗团队一起审查治疗方案。前列腺癌是男性&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/qnPqYWDze_F-KrR6NqnPLCE2OT3OTSlvFQTY2Qngfi2g_4P8raUIQF1rVPEeLIq_2dZOQEYhV7knC3NAp1LBBwoHRZuMzXaK3KIdgCfspW2jAxGOmuGhfr_IIbiK-OSfbV28SnyPEd2WJZIunFOMmxMWAOH5u4E8BDWom-ApHEjhM0tY4WqSo9i6t8dAbQAbhjW6B4AFt-_Mofy3dGZSwMSOUq6ZaODYGRI1xLOGdfSyY9VjQFNIptsGf1GfPU51rDBfGYl3llZtn_6nrtxhbaWDiA/pyWIPZynIk6TuU3j0pwtvwM2g5wjOTLr/9" target="_blank"&gt;最常见的癌症之一&lt;/a&gt;，尤其是随着年龄的增长，但在过去的几十年中，生存率有所提高。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）说，他今天将与弗拉基米尔·普京（Vladimir Putin）打电话&lt;/strong&gt;， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/y3dLNwY3ffJnLkpJjDBQMFeEGOh6hSm6b2EmhDbACfwTqIzFMOhiC7gCxF3UEqD-yjH7nCHNCtHf4yvd64PX5QZtG04LhdiDcMxy6wK4wMiVYv_GJgBqs-vCIcuD_AM10eSIC9jRcNeEMsunl1uGWMhZKTRLV59jgIKwSKOnx7WEgHT57Rb8Sf8CNwmM7qVpqM0x6onLFoeVSl6kd4Gr8APcrlMj2b4e9uBzwIADiVX564qPIpdxyTIQVFoBvUGa7tvX0EfrVnPkRzK2XAQoAU83bA/lfKDHAAYM7uBngt340PEHOPhL-GAls3s/9" target="_blank"&gt;讨论乌克兰战争的结局&lt;/a&gt;。据说这位俄罗斯总统认为他有一个强有力的手，因此&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/7kf5lWgJNpPu6j_qbmsfoXy7ZYxTydD0OhpEYZUnOvxrQr-jzQIL6XrPN9JaNucMx_HiUSPwZCnKlBR-dg-LFqaOkQney-wKGImE-m1Sced6aWEkUpSzpY2jkWl-4mNqJ4ufKbAV1VXjMD0eSNkpXGtgKOx0BWKLSi_mh_FwTSsoCJpzEyN8n16u1SdUo1-kBDJxaszkifTDV2St9vjSk9f2r1o1yikXu69QNfR6jMr0C30dabGTnInzpBXhdKiv39SyQCNwb7b9bt8IAz9B0jwYxA/p2FN6jcQiLU8WF3Jn5Zm7dVIc4l42rR6/9" target="_blank"&gt;可能不会通过让步提供太多&lt;/a&gt;。同时，乌克兰总统沃迪米尔·泽伦斯基（Volodymyr Zelenskiy） &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/UWmkJp_9koivjiA19IHJ2REnFxrQOWG7sbYGAIAm2K3ic7GGbZ04P03RwDTYqOoQ3TboAqkncyJswEAEsO89OiweTxJxjVKNB8qelmZ8z6t7atZ008C4aU65LSzCPfaqZJq_ZowT8t8I3HBhO-QCXxBJ-ZWUTHBSDTaGw-8uDzP8QF7c-kWyrZ7-SbExdNlHFhMcfLxJKwCW7Rqq0WJb-Z_xWH7GTQ0k5XCggO2p4I1D1NTsX65XIDbpSVt89xAdU5UYKO8LA1JDbQtknoPRbHZB2w/Mi-qfgBMCx1DjMrsgVV1VmMMUPpJ71zg/9" target="_blank"&gt;与罗马的JD Vance进行了交谈&lt;/a&gt;，这是他们自2月份&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/EHZ1IqnNsODX8kbf4C_c5uS8EOtKVMMeLFMtZkKxsxceGYgi_c3clSvyo3J2ZEgLiBR1Jw21zDUT9h3yPJQ_7NvtvZ89_gzLfD7R31QyG5mIL8SAiWKvee1alYQ1NBlK3DDr-0z2Aqxlt9iAuKFqWF8lKc-fcahZ2NiUejnsPoGBybYa-z8hcSGBB52ACmAU0i2kDXiwSioYPMC4Bg4pbr2yuLEyFnzp5JsbQOpO6-dyruyXVJ3B-I5jcX6kWBePPWkHmMtyPwyL9I-nSWQ8A5fkTg/ja8SY8Pb_1o_3oNjFRs7B5cp181jp-Sm/9" target="_blank"&gt;笨拙的椭圆形办公室争吵&lt;/a&gt;以来的第一次会议。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="font-family: Georgia, serif; margin: 16px 0;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;抱歉，新泽西通勤者。&lt;/strong&gt; NJ Transit及其机车工程师&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/i0c-jElb4yH9nXhDoDKPxObGezkX25LWQxu4BEY2zAwEq3YIJeoe2j2z_CNeP6rC4dVAEJl1z1bMvheqy3EduIyBGg5_q4-55PJ-We-FOZx4-tCx4JfYc7UHykCT09kX-Vha8mEn8ouhv82Cfbk0eBXpnW5XyMB4i_bTwh2CzPA8bfcAnTVNqeJWyM4x4NyQAemmJyNkeFFDFYM0sXedcKLZXeUbvUeoraBwsqynaoQpPQK1gskiPyUZHFnZ-0Jyk2ry3dsX3gaD22qDVYth41HBpw/UC2ABAq8BsdoTrvvQwiYqZBXLV6sO5YY/9" target="_blank"&gt;达成了一项新合同的协议&lt;/a&gt;，结束了为期三天的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/XhCsAL8mbeAg7iybY33IGsXBj0kA152BDfCp9Ty-eaNIBEZv6_Ppv8K8Nxw7ca5ts-fYtvN7HqBXpGDrCtSR0I9wZ3etQ4q7eMbk-H9y676_qgGnr8ca01PjQoX2OY_TwyQ4d-YLPTDcIYs3EpXAThzfkuaQwRqlymwd11_69z7i4tKm33nlKrp4dP4yz6wwE1ceK-KOL7bvuHiQ64M8aKiT6GmWKKRsAm6RjhQ2f2dmKM8aFFQTMuLLO9K18iTuvLdc1aHtu5OZOxHUhhTpbYat_A/NJ1Nif06fO5K551VSIJYSyKLbDRVtgIk/9" target="_blank"&gt;公交罢工，破坏了数千名车手的火车&lt;/a&gt;，但&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/aK2p59V_tivVbugy14nAuw5kE6Znsgi