e="font-family: Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;"&gt;这些变化正在为这些美国人的比赛加剧&lt;/strong&gt;，并在非洲大陆的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/KT9gSswL5f5RJxs2-W2uqgrrKD7d_8xxqzOWExmXp43j7P59XMErZXAspPRWTpADvgaJO5nHWVB-FUOMhhISERQNDgzZP90ZyvZY9ZNms38ps4vvSBKtI3kUjXCE0RQG4zym_O0_-H5a0UneemxZ52OAs4Axh3RFuwNOwG8EUo_m9UO0RLYLO6p8f2aznOvcMzQw3UsO09SzWv_KM0825ELLRccsR8qtV6LTHwPXuoZmRwYKV8i5B1KT4qaagguT5P5ha_5QHUCWggoQ7xtf3dRiUQ/UlZdzrxiVFBfw2yDxiBRtmY5KZ909u_F/9" target="_blank"&gt;居住&lt;/a&gt;地清楚地射击，以确保签证和护照在他们仍然可以的情况下获得签证和护照。&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;div class="body-image" style="margin: 20px 0px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/gXIqq-_N6haczgDCU9HJbRg_INjriDZBdXYPGYTTLxMpIhGQ8e1ld2SrW9yUYxZGw5ySlbcOaJxNXHZxvjE9Th0z01_BW7GpXCVXmY6qSsqPLGw7yWEFKA4XqpDEtev9QnLmHhHEKVx_nqVUnKA6AlhDy-3lgPB6nt3qBdR3ZwQMMocrsMUc0tTyyKaqLHtdMISW0m_H79AqKgFD3ISXpBYHqGq1H5AoZqrQe19E6pAdQ7h9N15Sml-c8hcB2M962eYyB4Jwvi_V4gn_QgEyw3rYNw/cT13qMVL4eqgvViixYa0zo4qqNnuIcb9/9" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="550"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img alt="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-05-19/americans-escaping-trump-race-to-secure-european-citizenship" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iYNqZqykBp20/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" width="550"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt; &lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-05-19/americans-escaping-trump-race-to-secure-european-citizenship" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iYNqZqykBp20/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="display: block; width: 530px; margin: auto;" width="530" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td style="border-collapse: collapse; padding: 0px 10px;"&gt;&lt;table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width=